{"tid":1526161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同學各位搵個位，這是狗的開學禮","createTime":"2019-09-01T04:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T07:08:40.000Z","uid":78392,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2992d211ff451cfe8876a99da66d347d28bc7535","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:32:57.000Z","msg":"求下所有同學仔<br />\n就算你唔夠膽動武禍必及家人<br />\n<br />\n請你一定要杯葛佢地<br />\n<br />\n唔好再怕仼何咩人際關係<br />\n都唔好以為啲狗仔有係ig係同路人就放過<br />\n<br />\n父債子還<br />\n作為狗仔想做同路人就一定要做前線先算還債<br />\n<br />\n我求下你地<br />\n如果開學之後<br />\n啲狗仔無事<br />\n班狗只會更恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">父債子還<br />\n杯葛狗仔</span></span>"},{"pid":"c88eea42a5d287d6033c092b213bdd13aeb5484d","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51cik7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51cik7n.jpg&h=72475cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲膽心狗仔會係同路人？"},{"pid":"7e9ae30777ac4532747d0ba46f07b7ff43c6567e","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPJp07F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPJp07F.jpg&h=46d056dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢為我哋無咗隻眼<br />\n你連杯葛都唔夠膽做？"},{"pid":"7e5e3d66422bdc16459cfdaddeeeadf89e6e6ca6","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AzaoxeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzaoxeL.jpg&h=f4202c41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都已經俾狗性暴力<br />\n你仲膽心人際關係嗎？"},{"pid":"929ee6076ba36d549cb915999f4306024123eb42","tid":1526161,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c88eea42a5d287d6033c092b213bdd13aeb5484d","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51cik7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51cik7n.jpg&h=72475cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲膽心狗仔會係同路人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n吹大雞每個站都黎個大清洗<br />\n等狗鐵永久不能運作 齊齊唔洗返工 仲正過塞機場<br />\n唔通爆黑社會麻雀館 就係極限? 黑社會定係狗鐵(政府)仆街D?<br />\n塞鐵已經無用 要直接令全港狗鐵收皮<br />\n今晚咁既下場 就係狗鐵害既 其實都唔止今晚<br />\n你估落去屌D職員有用? 咪撚玩喇<br />\n跳閘? 加價都賺返有突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n站內鋪頭日日唔敢開 <br />\n列車運作唔到 無人坐 齊齊唔洗返工 一係排到仆街去坐巴士<br />\n無人敢再落廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n明明你地有能力 又咁容易 點解大家仲未收狗鐵皮?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523278</a>"},{"pid":"875b536fb71eab3547586db32049c827f8e3a03a","tid":1526161,"uid":201256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:37:48.000Z","msg":"無視佢地已經夠<br />\n合法合情合理<br />\n如果你係勇武, 出手都係可以體諒"},{"pid":"ba07caef4836bb712f551705bcdc22c097f436c1","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iTwOJni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiTwOJni.jpg&h=79f96acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有學霸係狗仔<br />\n你怕無人carry你？<br />\n放心<br />\n大把師兄師姐會幫你"},{"pid":"995b36cb92ff10b181cda9322b08d4443c48f1cf","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ak3miWf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fak3miWf.png&h=05792296&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"646fc405d3b1839f12dd3b46bcfbe2d188e42c1d","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cTxqBr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cTxqBr.jpg&h=020ed9c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGyhBH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGyhBH6.jpg&h=b9f6778f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你既好朋友係狗仔<br />\n唔忍心杯葛佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我求你哋</span></span><br />\n用最理性既方法<br />\n話俾你既狗仔好朋友聽<br />\n唔一定係你既錯<br />\n只係你既家人摧毁太多香港人<br />\n只要香港警察認錯<br />\n承擔自己嘅惡果<br />\n我就會同你做返朋友"},{"pid":"7942ffa50f9240508b4c30279bd2cc21ec9c3132","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thPQckq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthPQckq.png&h=8e47e047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各位同學仔<br />\n請一定要杯葛殺人狗既仔女"},{"pid":"a9e4940b64781a2fd897504a7700e8020003bdf0","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2voxqX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2voxqX.png&h=56a958f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求下大家<br />\n唔好再再以為狗仔係同路人就放過"},{"pid":"589d31d690aecc9f3e79b8fe1ee8924fc658aeb2","tid":1526161,"uid":293539,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"仲有心情作on9歌 小朋大出齊毛未"},{"pid":"2ced569b85842ee4168908d5b0b0a43b49087c36","tid":1526161,"uid":78392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"589d31d690aecc9f3e79b8fe1ee8924fc658aeb2","tid":1526161,"uid":293539,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"仲有心情作on9歌 小朋大出齊毛未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:16:51.000Z","msg":"你覺得似歌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分段清晰啲咋喎"},{"pid":"60447579c1506771c682a2c1d261ea5c2af96fe2","tid":1526161,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike